Complete Detailed Parts List
1. Microcontrollers & Development Boards
1.1 Arduino Uno R3
Model: Arduino Uno R3

Microcontroller: ATmega328P

Operating Voltage: 5V

Input Voltage: 7-12V

Digital I/O Pins: 14 (6 PWM outputs)

Analog Input Pins: 6

Flash Memory: 32 KB

SRAM: 2 KB

EEPROM: 1 KB

Clock Speed: 16 MHz

Purpose: Primary controller for outdoor sensing unit

1.2 ESP32 Development Board
Model: ESP32-WROOM-32

Core: Xtensa® dual-core 32-bit LX6 microprocessor

Operating Voltage: 3.3V

Input Voltage: 5V via micro-USB

Wi-Fi: 802.11 b/g/n

Bluetooth: Bluetooth 4.2

SRAM: 520 KB

Flash Memory: 4 MB

GPIO Pins: 36

ADC Pins: 18 (12-bit)

Clock Speed: Up to 240 MHz

Purpose: Indoor ground unit with Wi-Fi connectivity

2. Environmental Sensors
2.1 BMP280 Digital Pressure Sensor
Type: Digital barometric pressure sensor

Interface: I2C (also supports SPI)

Operating Voltage: 1.8V - 3.6V

Pressure Range: 300-1100 hPa

Relative Accuracy: ±1.0 hPa

Absolute Accuracy: ±1.0 hPa

Temperature Range: -40°C to +85°C

Temperature Accuracy: ±1.0°C

Current Consumption: 2.7 μA @1Hz

Package: LGA package with metal lid

Purpose: Atmospheric pressure measurement

2.2 DHT22 Temperature & Humidity Sensor
Alternative Name: AM2302

Type: Digital temperature and humidity sensor

Interface: Single-wire serial

Operating Voltage: 3.3V - 6V

Temperature Range: -40°C to 80°C

Temperature Accuracy: ±0.5°C

Humidity Range: 0-100% RH

Humidity Accuracy: ±2% RH (25°C)

Resolution: 16-bit

Sampling Rate: 0.5 Hz (2 seconds)

Dimensions: 27mm x 59mm x 13.5mm

Purpose: Temperature and humidity measurement

2.3 GYML8511 UV Light Sensor
Type: Analog UV light sensor

Spectral Response: 280-390nm

Output Type: Analog voltage

Output Range: 0-1V

Operating Voltage: 3.3V - 5V

UV Intensity Range: 0-15 mW/cm²

Viewing Angle: 60 degrees

Response Time: 0.5 seconds

Purpose: UV index measurement

3. Custom-Built Weather Instruments
3.1 Anemometer (Wind Speed Sensor)
Electronic Components:

Hall Effect Sensor: A3144 (x1)

Type: Unipolar Hall Effect switch

Operating Voltage: 4.5V to 24V

Output Current: 25mA

Operating Temperature: -40°C to 85°C

Magnets: Neodymium magnets (x3), 5mm diameter

Bearings: 608ZZ ball bearings (x1)

Mechanical Components:

Cups: 3D printed or plastic cups (x3), 75mm diameter

Arm Assembly: PVC or aluminum arms

Mounting Shaft: Stainless steel shaft, 3mm diameter

Enclosure: Weatherproof ABS enclosure

3.2 Wind Vane (Direction Sensor)
Electronic Components:

Hall Effect Sensors: A3144 (x8)

Magnet: Ring magnet with multiple poles

Voltage Divider Resistors: 10kΩ resistors (x8)

Mechanical Components:

Vane Body: 3D printed or lightweight plastic

Shaft: Stainless steel, 4mm diameter

Bearings: 685ZZ miniature ball bearings

Direction Markers: N, NE, E, SE, S, SW, W, NW

3.3 Tipping Bucket Rain Gauge
Electronic Components:

Reed Switch: Normally open magnetic reed switch

Magnet: Small neodymium magnet

Water Collection Funnel: 150mm diameter

Mechanical Components:

Bucket Mechanism: Balanced tipping buckets (x2)

Bucket Capacity: 0.2mm rain per tip

Body: UV-resistant ABS plastic

Mounting Bracket: Adjustable leveling bracket

4. Supporting Components
4.1 RTC DS1302 Real-Time Clock
Chip: DS1302

Interface: 3-wire serial

Operating Voltage: 2.0V to 5.5V

Clock Accuracy: ±2ppm from 0°C to 40°C

Backup Battery: CR2032 3V lithium cell

Battery Life: More than 10 years

Purpose: Timekeeping during power outages

4.2 A3144 Hall Effect Sensors (Additional)
Quantity: 10 pieces (2 spare)

Type: Unipolar Hall Effect switch

Operating Voltage: 4.5V to 24V

Output Type: Digital (open collector)

Operating Point: Typical 30 Gauss

Release Point: Typical 20 Gauss

Response Time: 1.5 μs

4.3 Power Supply Components
Outdoor Unit:

Voltage Regulator: LM7805 5V regulator

Input Voltage: 9V-12V DC

Power Jack: DC 2.1mm jack

Capacitors: 100μF electrolytic, 0.1μF ceramic

Weatherproof Enclosure: IP65 rated box

Indoor Unit:

USB Power Supply: 5V 2A wall adapter

Micro-USB Cable: 1 meter

4.4 Communication Components
Serial Communication:

Cable: 4-conductor shielded cable, 5 meters

Connectors: 4-pin waterproof connectors

Level Shifter: Bidirectional logic level converter 3.3V-5V

Wi-Fi Antenna:

Type: PCB antenna (built into ESP32)

Range: Up to 100 meters in open space

5. Structural & Mechanical Components
5.1 Main Mounting Pole
Material: Galvanized steel or aluminum

