5.3 Enclosures & Protection
Outdoor Electronics Box:

Size: 200mm x 150mm x 80mm

Material: ABS plastic with IP65 rating

Cable Glands: PG7 waterproof cable glands (x6)

Ventilation: Breathable waterproof vents

Sensor Cable:

Type: 4-core shielded outdoor cable

Length: 5 meters

Color: Black UV-resistant

Connectors: Waterproof 4-pin connectors

